After installing this package, it is necessary to install some perl modules; install them as follow:

sudo cpan install Chipcard::PCSC::Card module
sudo cpan install Glib module
sudo cpan install Gtk3 module
sudo cpan install Locale::TextDomain module

To be able to use gscriptor with qt-sudo:

sudo sed -i 's|Exec=gscriptor|Exec=qt-sudo gscriptor|' /usr/share/applications/gscriptor.desktop

And that's it.

Enjoy
